[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=154157 On the DD-WRT forums] :This device appears to be able to use the DIR-300vB firmware. The included power adapter is an '''Amigo''' AM51-0501200FU. ID/OD/Len measurements are approximate. The ASIN and UPC for this device is probably identical the v2. ==Images== File:Keebox_W150NR_board_top.jpg|board top [[Has images::internal| ]] ==Serial== ===Boot log===
